text: David Powell (born 8 April 1991) is an Australian table tennis player. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's singles event, in which he was eliminated in the preliminary round by Marcelo Aguirre, and as part of the Australian team in the men's team event. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic table tennis players of Australia Category:Australian male table tennis players Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Table tennis players at the 2018 Commonwealth Games
